## Stepper

**Classes**: `tl-stepper`
**Sizes**: `tl-stepper--lg`, `tl-stepper--sm`
**Direction**: `tl-stepper--horizontal`, `tl-stepper--vertical`
**Label**: `tl-stepper--label-below`, `tl-stepper--label-aside`, `tl-stepper--hide-labels`

```html
<div class="tl-stepper tl-stepper--horizontal tl-stepper--lg">
  <ol class="tl-stepper__list">
    <li class="tl-stepper__step tl-stepper__step--success">
      <span class="tl-stepper__node"></span>
      <span class="tl-stepper__label">Step 1</span>
    </li>
    <li class="tl-stepper__step tl-stepper__step--current">
      <span class="tl-stepper__node">2</span>
      <span class="tl-stepper__label">Step 2</span>
    </li>
    <li class="tl-stepper__step tl-stepper__step--upcoming">
      <span class="tl-stepper__node">3</span>
      <span class="tl-stepper__label">Step 3</span>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
```

Step states: `tl-stepper__step--success`, `tl-stepper__step--error`, `tl-stepper__step--current`, `tl-stepper__step--upcoming`

